<h2 id="api">API</h2>

<h3 id="parameters">Parameters</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><code>items</code> - Array of navigation menu items (required)</li>
    <li><code>class</code> - Additional CSS classes</li>
    <li><code>attrs</code> - Additional HTML attributes</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p><strong>Item structure:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>label</code> - The text to display for the menu item</li>
    <li><code>href</code> - URL for simple link items</li>
    <li><code>content</code> - Array of content items for dropdown menus</li>
    <li><code>grid</code> - Boolean to enable grid layout for content</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p><strong>Content item structure:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>type</code> - <code>'link'</code> or <code>'feature'</code></li>
    <li><code>title</code> - Title of the content item</li>
    <li><code>description</code> - Description text (optional)</li>
    <li><code>href</code> - URL for the content item</li>
    <li><code>icon</code> - Icon name (optional)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h3 id="events">Events</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <p>The navigation menu component dispatches the following custom events:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>basecoat:initialized</code> - Fired when the navigation menu is initialized</li>
    <li><code>basecoat:navigation-menu:open</code> - Fired when a dropdown menu opens
      <ul>
        <li><code>detail.trigger</code> - The trigger element</li>
        <li><code>detail.content</code> - The content element</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li><code>basecoat:navigation-menu:close</code> - Fired when a dropdown menu closes</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h3 id="keyboard-navigation">Keyboard Navigation</h3>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Tab</strong> - Moves focus to the next focusable element</li>
    <li><strong>Shift + Tab</strong> - Moves focus to the previous focusable element</li>
    <li><strong>Escape</strong> - Closes any open dropdown and returns focus to trigger</li>
    <li><strong>Arrow Down</strong> - Opens dropdown and moves focus to first item</li>
    <li><strong>Arrow Left/Right</strong> - Moves focus between menu triggers</li>
    <li><strong>Enter/Space</strong> - Activates the focused element</li>
  </ul>
</section>

